---
Source:
  - Title: The Essential Mystics, Poets, Saints and Sages
    ISBN: 978-1571746931
By: Abu-Said Abil-Kheir
Page: 175
---
The pain of separation from God
is felt equally by a monk with his beads
and a drunk in a tavern.
This is an open wound that will
ultimately guide you to your heart of hearts.
